data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: The picture illustrates a harmonious relationship between humans and nature. There are three people standing by the water, and the lake reflects their reflections as well as the reflection of the bush. The leftmost person is standing up straight, and the person in the middle is bending her waist and putting her hands on her knees. Both of them are looking in the rightmost person's direction. The rightmost person is crouching and is looking down to the ground. All three people are positioned in nature and surrounded by the bush and the lake.
